Data Sync Limits and Considerations

You can include up to 100 objects for sync. If you are currently extracting more than 100 objects in your dataflows, contact Salesforce Customer Support before you enable data sync.
Data Sync only performs one sync per object. Keep this limit in mind if you must perform multiple syncs from the same object.

Considerations When Creating or Updating Dataflows with Data Sync

Considerations When Using CRM Analytics Templated Apps with Data Sync
